display_name: Sleep Habits (Sleep Heart Health Study Visit One (SHHS1)): Frequency of snoring
description: How often do you snore? 0=Do not snore any more, 1=Rarely-less than 1 night/wk, 2=Sometimes-1 or 2 nights/wk,3=Frequently-3 to 5nights/wk, 4=Always or almost always-6 or 7nights/wk, 8=Don't know
